OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly morning cloud and mist
OL,6,Faround coasts and hills could allow
OL,7,Ffor the odd spot of drizzle, but
OL,8,Fsaying dry for most. Cloud breaks to
OL,9,Fgive warm sunny spells by the
OL,10,Fafternoon, but staying cloudier near
OL,11,Fcoasts. Winds remaining light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine and dry evening for
OL,14,Fmost but with cloud along the coasts.
OL,15,FCloud builds inland overnight with
OL,16,Fpatchy coastal drizzle possible. Light
OL,17,Fnortherly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
