OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy with patchy drizzle
OL,6,Fpossible through the morning. Sunny
OL,7,Fspells developing through the
OL,8,Fafternoon and into the evening. Light
OL,9,Fto moderate northerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA fine
OL,12,Fand dry day on Sunday with moderate
OL,13,Fnortherly winds. Cloudier through
OL,14,FMonday and Tuesday with potential for
OL,15,Fpatchy rain at times and light
OL,16,Fnortherly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
